      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "The pain and exhaustion you feel are real and valid, yet holding onto this feeling keeps you trapped in a cycle that cannot end. The world might feel cold to you right now, but the right people and professional support can offer a connection that bridges even the deepest gaps. Letting go of the burden of carrying the grief alone doesn't mean abandoning your story; it means finding a new chapter where you are finally seen and held.",
